            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/openai-adds-real-time-video-function-to-chatgpt-advanced-voice-mode-which-can-quickly-explain-the-content-of-images-captured-by-mobile-phones-121854390.html</guid>
